OL,3,CFormer Post Office executive to appear
OL,4,Cat Horizon scandal inquiry
OL,6,FFormer Post Office boss Angela van den
OL,7,FBogerd will appear in front of the
OL,8,Fgovernment inquiry into the Horizon
OL,9,Fscandal on Thursday.
OL,11,FShe was a key figure in the events as
OL,12,Fthe former people services director at
OL,13,FPost Office Ltd and programme director
OL,14,Ffor the branch support programme.
OL,16,FThe Post Office has come under fire
OL,17,Fsince the broadcast of ITV drama Mr
OL,18,FBates Vs The Post Office, which put
OL,19,Fthe Horizon scandal under the
OL,20,Fspotlight.
