OL,6,FMs van den Bogerd, played by
OL,7,FCoronation Street star Katherine
OL,8,FKelly, features heavily in the series.
OL,10,FThe Horizon scandal led to hundreds of
OL,11,Fsub-postmasters being wrongly
OL,12,Fconvicted of fraud as a faulty IT
OL,13,Fsystem made it appear that they had
OL,14,Flost money.
OL,16,FThis led to the Post Office taking
OL,17,Fthem to court, resulting in them being
OL,18,Fjailed or fined.
