OL,6,FEarlier in April , revealed Angela Van
OL,7,FDen Bogerd, was told in January 2015
OL,8,Fthat the organisation had "materially
OL,9,Fmisled" the courts in prosecuting Carl
OL,10,FPage - a sub-postmaster from
OL,11,FStaffordshire.
OL,13,FMs Van Den Bogerd is heard in the
OL,14,Frecording agreeing with independent
OL,15,Finvestigator Ron Warmington that "we
OL,16,Fneed to take another look at this,"
OL,17,Fconfirming he had provided "further
OL,18,Finformation that is material to this
OL,19,Fcase".
