OL,6,FSecret tapes, obtained by ITV News
OL,7,Fshow Ms Van Den Bogerd was warned of
OL,8,Fwrongful conviction six years before
OL,9,Fan innocent sub-postmaster was cleared
OL,11,FHowever, Mr Page heard nothing from Ms
OL,12,FVan Den Bogerd or anyone at the Post
OL,13,FOffice after this meeting. His
OL,14,Fconviction was not overturned for
OL,15,Fanother six years.
OL,17,FIn that time, Mr Page attempted to
OL,18,Ftake his own life due to the impact
OL,19,Fthe wrongful conviction had on his
OL,20,Fmental health and his life.
