OL,6,FLess than four weeks after the meeting
OL,7,Fbetween Ms Van Den Bogerd and Mr
OL,8,FWarmington, she was called to give
OL,9,Fevidence to MPs about Horizon
OL,10,Falongside then Post Office chief
OL,11,Fexecutive Paula Vennells.
OL,13,FShe sat next to Ms Vennells as the
OL,14,FPost Office boss told the committee
OL,15,Fthat the organisation had found no
OL,16,Fevidence of any miscarriages of
OL,17,Fjustice.
