OL,6,FMs Van Den Bogerd told MPs there is
OL,7,F"not a culture of denial" at the Post
OL,8,FOffice, "we have not dragged our feet"
OL,9,Fand that she had "done a thorough
OL,10,Finvestigation" into hundreds of cases.
OL,12,FITV News approached Ms Van Den Bogerd
OL,13,Ffor comment.
OL,15,FShe said: "I am cooperating fully with
OL,16,Fthe Inquiry and will be giving
OL,17,Fevidence later this month. I will not
OL,18,Fbe making any comment outside the
OL,19,FInquiry process."
