OL,6,FA Post Office spokesperson said: "We
OL,7,Freiterate our heartfelt apology to
OL,8,Fvictims in the Horizon IT Scandal and
OL,9,Four focus remains on supporting the
OL,10,Fongoing Public Inquiry to establish
OL,11,Fthe truth of what happened so those
OL,12,Faffected can receive the justice and
OL,13,Fredress they so deserve."
OL,15,FSecond Sight's Mr Warmington told ITV
OL,16,FNews he could not comment on the
OL,17,Frecording as he has been designated a
OL,18,FCore Participant in the ongoing Post
OL,19,FOffice Inquiry and have undertaken
OL,20,Fconfidentiality agreements.
